105
00:08:05,601 --> 00:08:07,011
Kadiaľ mohla ujsť?

106
00:08:08,011 --> 00:08:09,610
Čo tu robíte, Jae Chan?

107
00:08:13,511 --> 00:08:14,610
Poďme tadiaľto.

108
