požiadala o láskavosť.

305
00:19:30,860 --> 00:19:33,190
No... Týka sa to Hong Joo...

306
00:19:34,791 --> 00:19:37,130
Neviete prečo odišla z práce, však nie?

307
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,531
Mala sen,

308
00:19:41,900 --> 00:19:43,300
